{"tid":1574371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「討論post」勇武真係有用？","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T18:34:18.000Z","uid":78392,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51efcca02fc3c3a0271c76c951df91a8a8815ee7","tid":1574371,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係好撚有用！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝勇武！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">受小弟一拜</span></span><br />\nMon post狗可以死返出去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fa28d3864067cb4a0b7c1d0d83c74f1c139803","tid":1574371,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家先係重點</span><br />\n大家都知道今次嘅革命<br />\n一定會係長期作戰<br />\n所以我哋除咗勇武<br />\n同時都要和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">「經濟篇」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">罷買</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=wky8n63dbjte\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%3Figshid%3Dwky8n63dbjte&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=32d151af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=wky8n63dbjte</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yB8O8Vt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyB8O8Vt.png&h=b4281caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只支持良心小店</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkshoplist?igshid=1xmnaa2psu846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkshoplist%3Figshid%3D1xmnaa2psu846&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a5c500dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkshoplist?igshid=1xmnaa2psu846</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6CXhPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6CXhPa.png&h=cd50145e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/neoguidehk?igshid=1rxeesdznq62s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fneoguidehk%3Figshid%3D1rxeesdznq62s&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a7bdeb6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/neoguidehk?igshid=1rxeesdznq62s</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wX2f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wX2f1.png&h=097b4ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢2個黃藍地圖互補其短<br />\n2個都要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都要幫手報料<br />\n只要你用過一次就會係google map儲存<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7aYMKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7aYMKV.png&h=9fd1d28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AT6pHhn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAT6pHhn.png&h=9727e0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你試</span></span><br />\n大家都係有良知嘅香港人<br />\n平時可能比較少試食試用<br />\n不過要長期作戰<br />\n我哋要令到對家嘅經濟受損<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">level 1</span>經過無良商店，一定要試食試用，只用不買<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">level 2</span>自備日用品出街，例如水樽。<br />\n我就每次都會帶空水樽出街，然後去M記攞水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">level 3</span>路過無良餐廳攞多幾張籌令到食客以為要排長龍放棄。<br />\n建議攞多人數既籌，咁樣間餐廳就要hold住一張大枱<br />\n被迫同藍絲親友食無良餐廳食耐啲霸耐啲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">所有學生同我用長者咭</span><br />\n<br />\n利申 和理非 唔識得勇武戰略<br />\n咩打狗救人<br />\n咩五分鐘黃金時間<br />\n咩打波組隊舉手"},{"pid":"ec5196b5a6ba140523ec04e481bd609f8ad02dbe","tid":1574371,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a53e947a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7db56912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"64fdc97fe8c8b480acb9f4748c31f5d310c0e8d6","tid":1574371,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b2076c80b5148e79a75faf985cd5d67dacdb19","tid":1574371,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9969a85